{"tid":902942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！強國都有馬爾代夫無敵大海景！！！","createTime":"2018-11-15T07:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T09:36:29.000Z","uid":75969,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7f0282f86a9e0dfc0f77a21220d4cfa00c9a6716","tid":902942,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181115/photo/bkn-20181115124417250-1115_00952_001_01p.jpg?20181115131226\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181115124417250-1115_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20181115131226&h=84693c47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">廢棄礦坑形成的湖，湖水呈藍色，確實美如馬爾代夫。（互聯網）</span><br />\n<br />\n近日內地網絡熱傳一段，片中可見安徽蕪湖有一處湖泊，湖水呈漂亮的蔚藍色，猶如美麗的馬爾代夫海景，也像九寨溝水色耀目的海子。衞星地圖上亦有它的樣貌，形狀像一隻藍色海星。可是這個美景背後，卻是讓人搖頭嘆息的真相。<br />\n<br />\n這個看似美麗的藍色湖泊，實際上是白馬山採礦區廢棄的大型礦坑，周邊是光禿禿的石頭和裸露的礦體。附近居民稱，上世紀九十年代時這裏是石礦場，礦坑底距地面有七八十米深，其後停止開採，礦區的原住居民已經搬走多年。礦坑廢棄後，有人開始往礦坑裏傾倒各種生活垃圾、建築垃圾。後來礦坑聚雨成湖，最深處約有30多米，而湖水變成蔚藍色，是最近一年的事。<br />\n<br />\n蕪湖弋江環保分局近日表示，該處是白馬山採礦區一處礦坑，因水質呈鹹性，積水變成蔚藍色。對於藍色湖水是怎樣形成，居民表示不太清楚，但因這片蔚藍景色成為網民熱門話題，引來不少網民慕名而來看個究竟。<br />\n<br />\n弋江環保分局就指，由於該區域地勢複雜且陡峭，而且周邊地質情況不穩定，為安全計已設下圍欄，在湖的四周拉起了警戒帶，豎立了警示牌，更呼籲網友不要前去遊玩。當局已派出多架挖掘機和貨車，在附近清理水邊的碎石，整頓周邊環境。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181115/photo/bkn-20181115124417250-1115_00952_001_03b.jpg?20181115131226\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181115124417250-1115_00952_001_03b.jpg%3F20181115131226&h=b1b6a5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181115/photo/bkn-20181115124417250-1115_00952_001_04b.jpg?20181115131226\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181115124417250-1115_00952_001_04b.jpg%3F20181115131226&h=80ae929a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181115/bkn-20181115124417250-1115_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181115%2Fbkn-20181115124417250-1115_00952_001.html&d=GxiPe3%2BoLEteQwn1b8MQp49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5ccb1066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181115/bkn-20181115124417250-1115_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6c0205139bfe8d64b33a4d3fb0311a92a174246c","tid":902942,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"tiffany Blue<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c8118d35ed8249d0629f7a91784d7167cb31b7","tid":902942,"uid":18566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:46:27.000Z","msg":"強國blue lagoon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bc7a3546e32a25bb14323d14894b2af960958d","tid":902942,"uid":46407,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:47:45.000Z","msg":"插多幾枝枯枝 仲唔係 中國版 青池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0yn9ugav\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0yn9ugav&h=9954940b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcfb62fd2841be833470dc2e853a5fc94600e1f4","tid":902942,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:50:43.000Z","msg":"強國成個國家都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f4a33009205bd1691b4842e2687b1e179796f2","tid":902942,"uid":87973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:57:03.000Z","msg":"湖底由垃圾污染物建構而成, 強國人跳落去游水會唔會中毒死? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248b70823d